verance (film)|Severance]]''\n* ''[[Fast Food Nation (film)|Fast Food Nation]]''\n* ''[[Sione's Wedding|Samoan Wedding]]''\n* ''A Woman in Winter'' \n* ''[[Kidulthood]]'' \n* ''[[Glastonbury (film)|Glastonbury]]''\n\n===2007===\n* ''[[Battle for Haditha]]''  \n* ''[[Never Apologize]]''\n* ''[[Mister Lonely]]''\n* ''[[Control (2007 film)|Control]]''  \n* ''[[Moving Midway]]''\n* ''[[Becoming Jane]]''  \n* ''Kaluapapa Heavan''  \n* ''[[Joe Strummer: The Future Is Unwritten]]''\n\n===2008===\n* ''[[A Bunch of Amateurs]]''\n* ''[[Franklyn]]'' \n* ''[[Salvation (2008 film)|Salvation]]''\n* ''[[Genova (2008 film)|Genova]]''\n* ''[[Is Anybody There?]]'' \n* ''[[Brideshead Revisited (film)|Brideshead Revisited]]'' \n* ''[[Palermo Shooting]]'' \n* ''[[Of Time and the City]]'' \n* ''[[Impy's Island]]'' \n* ''[[Sunshine Cleaning]]'' \n* ''[[Two Fists, One Heart]]''\n\n===2009===\n* ''[[Nowhere Boy]]''\n* ''Oil City Confidential'' \n* ''[[Beyond the Pole]]'' \n* ''[[The Boys Are Back (film)|The Boys Are Back]]'' \n* ''[[Harry Brown (film)|Harry Brown]]''\n* ''[[Triage (film)|Triage]]''\n* ''[[Perrier's Bounty]]''\n* ''[[Creation (2009 film)|Creation]]'' \n* ''[[Mugabe and the White African]]'' \n* ''[[Empire of Silver (film)|Empire of Silver]]''\n* ''[[An Education]]''\n\n===2010===\n* ''[[Robinson in Ruins]]'' \n* ''[[Made in Dagenham]]'' \n* ''[[Super (2010 American film)|Super]]''\n* ''[[13 Assassins (2010 film)|13 Assassins]]''\n* ''[[Essential Killing]]''\n* ''[[Chico and Rita]]''\n* ''[[Black Death (film)|Black Death]]''\n* ''[[Thunder Soul]]''\n* ''[[It's a Wonderful Afterlife]]''\n\n===2011===\n* ''[[Diana Vreeland: The Eye Has to Travel]]'' \n* ''[[Roman Polanski: A Film Memoir]]''\n* ''[[You're Next]]'' \n* ''[[Wuthering Heights (2011 film)|Wuthering Heights]]'' \n* ''[[Shame (2011 film)|Shame]]''\n* ''[[A Dangerous Method]]''\n* ''[[Hara-Kiri: Death of a Samurai]]''\n* ''[[The Decoy Bride]]''\n* ''[[TT3D: Closer to the Edge]]'' \n* ''[[Pina (film)|Pina]]'' \n* ''[[Li