ir (2009 film)|Up in the Air]]'' as Alex Goran\n* [[Anna Kendrick]] \u2013 ''[[Up in the Air (2009 film)|Up in the Air]]'' as Natalie Keener\n* [[M\u00e9lanie Laurent]] \u2013 ''[[Inglourious Basterds]]'' as Shosanna Dreyfuss\n\n===Best Ensemble===\n'''''[[The Hangover]]'''''\n* ''[[Inglourious Basterds]]''\n* ''[[Precious (film)|Precious]]''\n* ''[[Star Trek (film)|Star Trek]]''\n* ''[[Zombieland]]''\n\n===Breakthrough Performance===\n'''[[Gabourey Sidibe]] \u2013 ''[[Precious (film)|Precious]]'' as Claireece \"Precious\" Jones'''\n* [[Anna Kendrick]] \u2013 ''[[Up in the Air (2009 film)|Up in the Air]]'' as Natalie Keener\n* [[Christian McKay]] \u2013 ''[[Me and Orson Welles]]'' as [[Orson Welles]]\n* [[Carey Mulligan]] \u2013 ''[[An Education]]'' as Jenny Mellor\n* [[Chris Pine]] \u2013 ''[[Star Trek (film)|Star Trek]]'' as [[James T. Kirk]]\n* [[Christoph Waltz]] \u2013 ''[[Inglourious Basterds]]'' as [[Hans Landa|Col. Hans Landa]]\n\n==2010==\n\n===Best Film===\n* '''''[[The Social Network]]'''''\n* ''[[127 Hours]]''\n* ''[[Inception]]''\n* ''[[The King's Speech]]''\n* ''[[Winter's Bone]]''\n\n===Best Director===\n'''[[Danny Boyle]] \u2013 ''[[127 Hours]]'''''\n* [[David Fincher]] \u2013 ''[[The Social Network]]''\n* [[Debra Granik]] \u2013 ''[[Winter's Bone]]''\n* [[Tom Hooper]] \u2013 ''[[The King's Speech]]''\n* [[Christopher Nolan]] \u2013 ''[[Inception]]''\n* [[Edgar Wright]] \u2013 ''[[Scott Pilgrim vs. the World]]''\n\n===Best Actor===\n'''[[Colin Firth]] \u2013 ''[[The King's Speech]]'' as [[George VI]]'''\n* [[Jeff Bridges]] \u2013 ''[[True Grit (2010 film)|True Grit]]'' as [[Rooster Cogburn (character)|Reuben \"Rooster\" Cogburn]]\n* [[Jesse Eisenberg]] \u2013 ''[[The Social Network]]'' as [[Mark Zuckerberg]]\n* [[James Franco]] \u2013 ''[[127 Hours]]'' as [[Aron Ralston]]\n* [[Ryan Gosling]] \u2013 ''[[Blue Valentine (film)|Blue Valentine]]'' as Dean Pereira\n\n===Best Actress===\n'''[[Jennifer Lawrence]] \u2013 ''[[Winter's Bone]]'' as Ree Dolly'''\