 Me In (film)|Let Me In]]'' as [[Hit-Girl]] and Abby\n* [[Mia Wasikowska]] \u2013 ''[[The Kids Are All Right (film)|The Kids Are All Right]]'' as Joni Allgood\n\n==2011==\n\n===Best Film===\n'''''[[The Artist (film)|The Artist]]'''''<ref name=det>{{cite web|title=Detroit Film Critics Society announces awards nominees; 'Take Shelter' leads with six nods|url=http://www.mlive.com/movies/index.ssf/2011/12/detroit_film_critics_society_a.html|website=MLive.com|accessdate=18 November 2016}}</ref>\n* ''[[The Descendants]]''\n* ''[[Hugo (film)|Hugo]]''\n* ''[[Take Shelter]]''\n* ''[[The Tree of Life (film)|The Tree of Life]]''\n\n===Best Director===\n'''[[Michel Hazanavicius]] \u2013 ''[[The Artist (film)|The Artist]]'''''<ref name=det />\n* [[Terrence Malick]] \u2013 ''[[The Tree of Life (film)|The Tree of Life]]''\n* [[Jeff Nichols]] \u2013 ''[[Take Shelter]]''\n* [[Martin Scorsese]] \u2013 ''[[Hugo (film)|Hugo]]''\n* [[Nicolas Winding Refn]] \u2013 ''[[Drive (2011 film)|Drive]]''\n\n===Best Actor===\n'''[[Michael Fassbender]] \u2013 ''[[Shame (2011 film)|Shame]]'' as Brandon Sullivan'''<ref name=det />\n* [[George Clooney]] \u2013 ''[[The Descendants]]'' as Matt King\n* [[Jean Dujardin]] \u2013 ''[[The Artist (film)|The Artist]]'' as George Valentin\n* [[Brad Pitt]] \u2013 ''[[Moneyball (film)|Moneyball]]'' as [[Billy Beane]]\n* [[Michael Shannon]] \u2013 ''[[Take Shelter]]'' as Curtis LaForche\n\n===Best Actress===\n'''[[Michelle Williams (actress)|Michelle Williams]] \u2013 ''[[My Week with Marilyn]]'' as [[Marilyn Monroe]]'''<ref name=det />\n* [[Viola Davis]] \u2013 ''[[The Help (film)|The Help]]'' as Aibileen Clark\n* [[Felicity Jones]] \u2013 ''[[Like Crazy (2011 film)|Like Crazy]]'' as Anna Maria Gardner\n* [[Meryl Streep]] \u2013 ''[[The Iron Lady (film)|The Iron Lady]]'' as [[Margaret Thatcher]]\n* [[Charlize Theron]] \u2013 ''[[Young Adult (film)|Young Adult]]'' as Mavis Gary\n\n===Best Supporting Actor===\n'''[[Christopher Plummer]] \u2013 ''[[Beginners]]'' as 