\n* [[Charlize Theron]] \u2013 ''[[Bombshell (2019 film)|Bombshell]]'' as [[Megyn Kelly]]\n* [[Ren\u00e9e Zellweger]] \u2013 ''[[Judy (film)|Judy]]'' as [[Judy Garland]]\n\n===Best Supporting Actor===\n'''[[Joe Pesci]] \u2013 ''[[The Irishman]]'' as [[Russell Bufalino]]'''\n* [[Willem Dafoe]] \u2013 ''[[The Lighthouse (2019 film)|The Lighthouse]]'' as Thomas Wake\n* [[Tom Hanks]] \u2013 ''[[A Beautiful Day in the Neighborhood]]'' as [[Fred Rogers]]\n* [[Brad Pitt]] \u2013 ''[[Once Upon a Time in Hollywood]]'' as Cliff Booth\n* [[Sam Rockwell]] \u2013 ''[[Richard Jewell (film)|Richard Jewell]]'' as Watson Bryant\n* [[Wesley Snipes]] \u2013 ''[[Dolemite Is My Name]]'' as [[D'Urville Martin]]\n\n===Best Supporting Actress===\n'''[[Laura Dern]] \u2013 ''[[Marriage Story]]'' as Nora Fanshaw'''\n* [[Kathy Bates]] \u2013 ''[[Richard Jewell (film)|Richard Jewell]]'' as Barbara \"Bobi\" Jewell\n* [[Scarlett Johansson]] \u2013 ''[[Jojo Rabbit]]'' as Rosie Betzler\n* [[Anna Paquin]] \u2013 ''[[The Irishman]]'' as Peggy Sheeran\n* [[Florence Pugh]] \u2013 ''[[Little Women (2019 film)|Little Women]]'' as Amy March\n\n===Best Ensemble===\n'''''[[Once Upon a Time in Hollywood]]'''''\n* ''[[Dolemite Is My Name]]''\n* ''[[The Farewell (2019 film)|The Farewell]]''\n* ''[[The Irishman]]''\n* ''[[Parasite (2019 film)|Parasite]]''\n\n===Breakthrough Performance===\n'''[[Florence Pugh]] \u2013 ''[[Fighting with My Family]]'', ''[[Midsommar (film)|Midsommar]]'', ''[[Little Women (2019 film)|Little Women]]'' (actress)'''\n* [[Ana de Armas]] \u2013 ''[[Knives Out (film)|Knives Out]]'', ''[[The Informer (2019 film)|The Informer]]'', ''[[Yesterday (2019 film)|Yesterday]]'' (actress)\n* [[Jessie Buckley]] \u2013 ''[[Wild Rose (film)|Wild Rose]]'', ''[[Judy (film)|Judy]]'' (actress)\n* [[Kaitlyn Dever]] \u2013 ''[[Booksmart]]'', ''[[Them That Follow]]'' (actress)\n* [[Aisling Franciosi]] \u2013 ''[[The Nightingale (2018 film)|The Nightingale]]'' (actress)\n* [[Paul Walter Hauser]] \u2013 ''[[Ri