e Square]]''\n* ''[[The Unknown Known]]''\n\n==2014==\n\n===Best Film===\n'''''[[Boyhood (film)|Boyhood]]'''''\n* ''[[Birdman (film)|Birdman]]''\n* ''[[The Grand Budapest Hotel]]''\n* ''[[Under the Skin (2013 film)|Under the Skin]]''\n* ''[[Whiplash (2014 film)|Whiplash]]''\n\n===Best Director===\n'''[[Richard Linklater]] \u2013 ''[[Boyhood (film)|Boyhood]]'''''\n* [[Wes Anderson]] \u2013 ''[[The Grand Budapest Hotel]]''\n* [[Damien Chazelle]] \u2013 ''[[Whiplash (2014 film)|Whiplash]]''\n* [[Jonathan Glazer]] \u2013 ''[[Under the Skin (2013 film)|Under the Skin]]''\n* [[Alejandro Gonz\u00e1lez I\u00f1\u00e1rritu|Alejandro G. I\u00f1\u00e1rritu]] \u2013 ''[[Birdman (film)|Birdman]]''\n\n===Best Actor===\n'''[[Michael Keaton]] \u2013 ''[[Birdman (film)|Birdman]]'' as Riggan Thomson'''\n* [[Benedict Cumberbatch]] \u2013 ''[[The Imitation Game]]'' as [[Alan Turing]]\n* [[Brendan Gleeson]] \u2013 ''[[Calvary (2014 film)|Calvary]]'' as Father James\n* [[Jake Gyllenhaal]] \u2013 ''[[Nightcrawler (film)|Nightcrawler]]'' as Louis \"Lou\" Bloom\n* [[Tom Hardy]] \u2013 ''[[Locke (film)|Locke]]'' as Ivan Locke\n* [[Eddie Redmayne]] \u2013 ''[[The Theory of Everything (2014 film)|The Theory of Everything]]'' as [[Stephen Hawking]]\n\n===Best Actress===\n'''[[Rosamund Pike]] \u2013 ''[[Gone Girl (film)|Gone Girl]]'' as Amy Elliott-Dunne'''\n* [[Essie Davis]] \u2013 ''[[The Babadook]]'' as Amelia\n* [[Scarlett Johansson]] \u2013 ''[[Under the Skin (2013 film)|Under the Skin]]'' as The Female\n* [[Julianne Moore]] \u2013 ''[[Still Alice]]'' as Dr. Alice Howland\n* [[Reese Witherspoon]] \u2013 ''[[Wild (2014 film)|Wild]]'' as [[Cheryl Strayed]]\n\n===Best Supporting Actor===\n'''[[J. K. Simmons]] \u2013 ''[[Whiplash (2014 film)|Whiplash]]'' as Terence Fletcher'''\n* [[Josh Brolin]] \u2013 ''[[Inherent Vice (film)|Inherent Vice]]'' as Lt. Det. Christian \"Bigfoot\" Bjornsen\n* [[Ethan Hawke]] \u2013 ''[[Boyhood (film)|Boyhood]]'' as Mason Evans, Sr.\n* [[Edward Norton]] \u2013 ''[[Birdman (film)|Birdman]]'' as Mike Shiner\n* [[Mark Ruffalo]] \u2013 ''[[Foxcatcher]]'' as [[Dave Schultz (wrestling)|Dave Schultz]]\n\n===Best Supporting Actress===\n'''[[Patricia Arquette]] \u2013 ''[[Boyhood (film)|Boyhood]]'' as Olivia Evans'''\n* [[Laura Dern]] \u2013 ''[[Wild (2014 film)|Wild]]'' as Barbara \"Bobbi\" Grey\n* [[Rene Russo]] \u2013 ''[[Nightcrawler (film)|Nightcrawler]]'' as Nina Romina\n* [[Emma Stone]] \u2013 ''[[Birdman (film)|Birdman]]'' as Sam Thomson\n* [[Tilda Swinton]] \u2013 ''[[Snowpiercer]]'' as Deputy-Minister Mason\n\n===Best Ensemble===\n'''''[[Birdman (film)|Birdman or (The Unexpected Virtue of Ignorance)]]'' (TIE)''' <br />\n'''''[[The Grand Budapest Hotel]]'' (TIE)''' <br />\n'''''[[Guardians of the Galaxy (film)|Guardians of the Galaxy]]'' (TIE)'''\n* ''[[Boyhood (film)|Boyhood]]''\n* ''[[Into the Woods (film)|Into the Woods]]''\n\n===Breakthrough Performance===\n'''[[Damien Chazelle]] \u2013 ''[[Whiplash (2014 film)|Whiplash]]''''' (director, screenplay)\n* [[Jennifer Kent]] \u2013 ''[[The Babadook]]'' (director, screenplay)\n* [[Gugu Mbatha-Raw]] \u2013 ''[[Belle (2013 film)|Belle]]'', ''[[Beyond the Lights]]'' (actress)\n* [[Chris Pratt]] \u2013 ''[[Guardians of the Galaxy (film)|Guardians of the Galaxy]]'' (actor)\n* [[Dan Stevens]] \u2013 ''[[The Guest (film)|The Guest]]'' (actor)\n\n===Best Screenplay===\n'''[[Richard Linklater]] \u2013 ''[[Boyhood (film)|Boyhood]]'''''\n* [[Wes Anderson]] \u2013 ''[[The Grand Budapest Hotel]]''\n* [[Damien Chazelle]] \u2013 ''[[Whiplash (2014 film)|Whiplash]]''\n* [[Alejandro Gonz\u00e1lez I\u00f1\u00e1rritu|Alejandro G. I\u00f1\u00e1rritu]], [[Nicol\u00e1s Giacobone]], [[Alexander Dinelaris Jr.]], and [[Armando B\u00f3 (screenwriter)|Armando B\u00f3]] \u2013 ''[[Birdman (film)|Birdman]]''\n* [[John Michael McDonagh]] \u2013 ''[[Calvary (2014 film)|Calvary]]''\n\n===Best Documentary===\n'''''[[Citizenfour]]'''''\n* ''[[Finding Vivian Maier]]''\n* ''[[Jodorowsky's Dune|Jodorowsky\u2019s Dune]]''\n* ''Keep On Keepin\u2019 On''\n* ''[[Life Itself (2014 film)|Life Itself]]''\n\n==2015==\n\n===Best Film===\n'''''[[Spotlight (film)|Spotlight]]'''\n* ''[[Brooklyn (film)|Brooklyn]]''\n* ''[[Inside Out (2015 film)|Inside Out]]''\n* ''[[Mad Max: Fury Road]]''\n* ''[[The Revenant (2015 film)|The Revenant]]''\n* ''[[Sicario (2015 film)|Sicario]]''\n* ''[[Youth (2015 film)|Youth]]''\n\n===Best Director===\n'''[[George Miller (director)|George Miller]] \u2013 ''[[Mad Max: Fury Road]]'''\n* [[John Crowley (director)|John Crowley]] \u2013 ''[[Brooklyn (film)|Brooklyn]]''\n* [[Alejandro Gonz\u00e1lez I\u00f1\u00e1rritu|Alejandro G. I\u00f1\u00e1rritu]] \u2013 ''[[The Revenant (2015 film)|The Revenant]]''\n* [[Tom McCarthy (director)|Tom McCarthy]] \u2013 ''[[Spotlight (film)|Spotlight]]''\n* [[Paolo Sorrentino]] \u2013 ''[[Youth (2015 film)|Youth]]''\n\n===Best Actor===\n'''[[Michael Caine]] \u2013 ''[[Youth (2015 film)|Youth]]'' as Fred Ballinger'''\n* [[Christopher Abbott]] \u2013 ''[[James White (film)|James White]]'' as James White\n* [[Leonardo DiCaprio]] \u2013 ''[[The Revenant (2015 film)|The Revenant]]'' as [[Hugh Glass]]\n* [[Michael Fassbender]] \u2013 ''[[Steve Jobs (film)|Steve Jobs]]'' as [[Steve Jobs]]\n* [[Tom Hardy]] \u2013 ''[[Legend (2015 film)|Legend]]'' as [[Kray twins|Ronnie and Reggie Kray]]\n\n===Best Actress===\n''' [[Saoirse Ronan]] \u2013 ''[[Brooklyn (film)|Brooklyn]]'' as Eilis Lacey\n* [[Cate Blanchett]] \u2013 ''[[Carol (film)|Carol]]'' as Carol Aird\n* [[Brie Larson]] \u2013 ''[[Room (2015 film)|Room]]'' as Joy 'Ma' Newsome\n* [[Jennifer Lawrence]] \u2013 ''[[Joy (film)|Joy]]'' as [[Joy Mangano]]\n* [[Bel Powley]] \u2013 ''[[The Diary of a Teenage Girl]]'' as Minnie Goetze\n\n===Best Supporting Actor===\n'''[[Liev Schreiber]] \u2013 ''[[Spotlight (film)|Spotlight]]'' as [[Martin Baron]]'''\n* [[Paul Dano]] \u2013 ''[[Love & Mercy (film)|Love & Mercy]]'' as [[Brian Wilson]]\n* [[Benicio del Toro]] \u2013 ''[[Sicario (2015 film)|Sicario]