ger Splash (2015 film)|A Bigger Splash]]'' as Harry Hawkes\n* [[Lucas Hedges]] \u2013 ''[[Manchester by the Sea (film)|Manchester by the Sea]]'' as Patrick Chandler\n\n===Best Supporting Actress===\n'''[[Viola Davis]] \u2013 ''[[Fences (film)|Fences]]'' as Rose Maxson (TIE)''' <br />\n'''[[Greta Gerwig]] \u2013 ''[[20th Century Women]]'' as Abbie (TIE)'''\n* [[Elle Fanning]] \u2013 ''[[20th Century Women]]'' as Julie\n* [[Felicity Jones]] \u2013 ''[[A Monster Calls (film)|A Monster Calls]]'' as Lizzie O'Malley\n* [[Michelle Williams (actress)|Michelle Williams]] \u2013 ''[[Manchester by the Sea (film)|Manchester by the Sea]]'' as Randi Chandler\n\n===Best Ensemble===\n'''''[[20th Century Women]]'''''\n* ''[[Everybody Wants Some!! (film)|Everybody Wants Some!!]]''\n* ''[[Hell or High Water (2016 film)|Hell or High Water]]''\n* ''[[Manchester by the Sea (film)|Manchester by the Sea]]''\n* ''[[Moonlight (2016 film)|Moonlight]]''\n\n===Breakthrough Performance===\n'''[[Kelly Fremon Craig]] \u2013 ''[[The Edge of Seventeen]]'' (director, screenplay)'''\n* [[Mahershala Ali]] \u2013 ''[[Moonlight (2016 film)|Moonlight]]'', ''[[Hidden Figures]]'' (actor)\n* [[Lucas Hedges]] \u2013 ''[[Manchester by the Sea (film)|Manchester by the Sea]]'' (actor)\n* [[Barry Jenkins]] \u2013 ''[[Moonlight (2016 film)|Moonlight]]'' (director, screenplay)\n* [[Trevante Rhodes]] \u2013 ''[[Moonlight (2016 film)|Moonlight]]'' (actor)\n* [[Trey Edward Shults]] \u2013 ''[[Krisha]]'' (director, screenplay)\n\n===Best Screenplay===\n'''[[Damien Chazelle]] \u2013 ''[[La La Land (film)|La La Land]]'''''\n* [[Eric Heisserer]] \u2013 ''[[Arrival (film)|Arrival]]''\n* [[Barry Jenkins]] \u2013 ''[[Moonlight (2016 film)|Moonlight]]''\n* [[Kenneth Lonergan]] \u2013 ''[[Manchester by the Sea (film)|Manchester by the Sea]]''\n* [[Taylor Sheridan]] \u2013 ''[[Hell or High Water (2016 film)|Hell or High Water]]''\n\n===Best Documentary===\n'''''[[O.J.: Made in America]]'''''\n* ''[[13th (film)|13th]]''\n* ''[[Gleason (2016 film)|Gleason]]''\n* ''[[Life, Animated]]''\n* ''[[Tickled]]''\n* ''[[Weiner (film)|Weiner]]''\n\n==2017==\n\n===Best Film===\n'''''[[The Florida Project]]'''''\n* ''[[The Disaster Artist (film)|The Disaster Artist]]''\n* ''[[Get Out]]''\n* ''[[The Shape of Water]]''\n* ''[[Three Billboards Outside Ebbing, Missouri]]''\n\n===Best Director===\n'''[[Sean Baker (filmmaker)|Sean Baker]] \u2013 ''[[The Florida Project]]'''''\n* [[Paul Thomas Anderson]] \u2013 ''[[Phantom Thread]]''\n* [[Guillermo del Toro]] \u2013 ''[[The Shape of Water]]''\n* [[Greta Gerwig]] \u2013 ''[[Lady Bird (film)|Lady Bird]]''\n* [[Christopher Nolan]] \u2013 ''[[Dunkirk (2017 film)|Dunkirk]]''\n* [[Jordan Peele]] \u2013 ''[[Get Out]]''\n\n===Best Actor===\n'''[[James Franco]] \u2013 ''[[The Disaster Artist (film)|The Disaster Artist]]'' as [[Tommy Wiseau]]'''\n* [[Timoth\u00e9e Chalamet]] \u2013 ''[[Call Me by Your Name (film)|Call Me by Your Name]]'' as Elio Perlman\n* [[Daniel Day-Lewis]] \u2013 ''[[Phantom Thread]]'' as Reynolds Woodcock\n* [[Gary Oldman]] \u2013 ''[[Darkest Hour (film)|Darkest Hour]]'' as [[Winston Churchill]]\n* [[Robert Pattinson]] \u2013 ''[[Good Time (film)|Good Time]]'' as Constantine \"Connie\" Nikas\n\n===Best Actress===\n'''[[Frances McDormand]] \u2013 ''[[Three Billboards Outside Ebbing, Missouri]]'' as Mildred Hayes'''\n* [[Jessica Chastain]] \u2013 ''[[Molly's Game]]'' as Molly Bloom\n* [[Sally Hawkins]] \u2013 ''[[The Shape of Water]]'' as Elisa Esposito\n* [[Margot Robbie]] \u2013 ''[[I, Tonya]]'' as [[Tonya Harding]]\n* [[Saoirse Ronan]] \u2013 ''[[Lady Bird (film)|Lady Bird]]'' as Christine \"Lady Bird\" McPherson\n\n===Best Supporting Actor===\n'''[[Willem Dafoe]] \u2013 ''[[The Florida Project]]'' as Bobby Hicks'''\n* [[Richard Jenkins]] \u2013 ''[[The Shape of Water]]'' as Giles\n* [[Sam Rockwell]] \u2013 ''[[Three Billboards Outside Ebbing, Missouri]]'' as Jason Dixon\n* [[Patrick Stewart]] \u2013 ''[[Logan (film)|Logan]]'' as [[Professor X|Cha